            </div>
            <h3>Downloadable files</h3>
            <p>Upload document files and create links to downloadable files like ZIP, PPT, PDF, and more from your HTML content.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-50">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
